Azad Azerbaijan Logo Azad Azerbaijan TV is a private television station in Azerbaijan. It has been broadcasting since December 25, 2000. ATV began broadcasting through movies and music videos, but later news, shows and other programmes were added. In the last years ATV claim to be the most popular and the most viewable channel in Azerbaijan. Source
